            mj-image(width='200px' src='https://i.ibb.co/VWS1Sfq/graph02-062024.png' alt='illustration de contrat signé')/
        mj-column(width='260px')
            mj-button(background-color='#BA4995' font-size='16px' line-height='20px' font-weight='500' inner-padding='8px 16px' border-radius='25px' css-class='hover' href='https://ecosup-assurance.fr/cv-book') Je télécharge
            mj-text(font-size='16px' font-weight='400' line-height='20px' container-background-color='#dadada') code pour accéder au CV Book : #[span(style='font-weight:700') CVBook062024]